- [ ] Events follow existing schema format
- [ ] Unit tests for reporter pass
- [ ] Integration test shows phase events in JSONL","status":"open","priority":3,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-27T17:21:37.332870142Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-27T17:35:20.389015202Z","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
